<lb n="0614a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0614a10" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1152</head>
<lb n="0614a11" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0614002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說佛母般若波羅蜜多大明觀
<lb n="0614a12" ed="T"/>想儀<note n="0614003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軌＋（經）【明】＊</note><app n="0614003"><lem>軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">軌經</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0614a13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0614a14" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0614004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0614004"><lem>西</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西</rdg></app>天<note n="0614005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔譯經〕－【明】</note><app n="0614005"><lem>譯經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏朝奉大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0614a15" ed="T"/>傳法大師<note n="0614006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔賜紫臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0614006"><lem>賜紫臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>施護奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0614a16" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT20p0614a1601">爾時世尊。普為一切修出世間最上悉地者。
<lb n="0614a17" ed="T"/>宣說佛母般若波羅蜜多大明觀想法。</p>
<lb n="0614a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614a1801">彼大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0614a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614a1901" type="dharani">那謨<note place="inline">引</note>婆&CB00344;&CB00085;帝<note place="inline">引一<note n="0614007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔句〕－【明】</note><app n="0614007"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>阿哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>倪
<lb n="0614a20" ed="T"/>也<note place="inline">二合引</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>囉彌多<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引二</note>阿波哩彌多虞拏
<lb n="0614a21" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引三</note>薄訖底<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;蹉邏<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引四</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0614a22" ed="T"/>合</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;多倪也<note place="inline">二合引</note>那波哩布哩多<note place="inline">引</note>曳
<lb n="0614a23" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引五</note>薩埵&CB00085;蹉邏<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引六</note>怛&CB00853;<note place="inline"><note n="0614008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切身＝寧也切【明】</note><app n="0614008"><lem>切身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">寧也切</rdg></app></note>他<note place="inline">引七</note>唵<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0614a24" ed="T"/>提<note place="inline">引八</note>率嚕<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">九</note>娑蜜哩<note place="inline">三合</note>底<note place="inline">十</note>尾惹曳<note place="inline">引
<lb n="0614a25" ed="T"/>十一</note>莎<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十二</note></p>
<lb n="0614a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614a2601">如是大明有大功德。最上最勝不可思議。諸
<lb n="0614a27" ed="T"/>修瑜伽行者。若欲觀想此大明字求悉地法。
<lb n="0614a28" ed="T"/>先當發起大菩提心。然後依法於自心上想淨
<lb n="0614a29" ed="T"/>月輪。於月輪中觀想提字。從臍輪轉於心而
<pb n="0614b" id="T20.1152.0614b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0614b01" ed="T"/>住。其字黃色是即般若波羅蜜多菩薩根本
<lb n="0614b02" ed="T"/>心字。如是想已。復想此字即成般若波羅蜜
<lb n="0614b03" ed="T"/>多菩薩。<note n="0614009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">想＝相【三】＊</note><note n="0614009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想＝相【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0614009"><lem>想</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">相</rdg></app>此菩薩<app source="0614009" type="＊"><lem>想</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">相</rdg></app>身真金色有其六臂。
<lb n="0614b04" ed="T"/>相好圓滿種種莊嚴頂戴寶冠。最上二手結
<lb n="0614b05" ed="T"/>說法印。其印以二手作合掌。二中指入掌內
<lb n="0614b06" ed="T"/>指面相合。二大指及二頭指。各各指面相捻。
<lb n="0614b07" ed="T"/>餘指不動成印。餘手持般若波羅蜜多經。優
<lb n="0614b08" ed="T"/>&CB00425;羅華。爍吉帝等。依法觀想如是想已。又復
<lb n="0614b09" ed="T"/>諦想般若波羅蜜多大明。最上甚深從無我
<lb n="0614b10" ed="T"/>生。由如是觀般若波羅蜜多無我生故。即一
<lb n="0614b11" ed="T"/>切法無我平等。以如是平等故。即從般若波
<lb n="0614b12" ed="T"/>羅蜜多。出生無邊諸文字相。文字相者攝一
<lb n="0614b13" ed="T"/>切相諸修瑜伽行者若聞。</p>
<lb n="0614b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b1401" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1D5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>提</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b15" ed="T"/>　二字</p>
<lb n="0614b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b1601">當於<note n="0614010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頂＝項【三】</note><note n="0614010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頂＝項【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0614010"><lem>頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">項</rdg></app>上而作觀想若聞。</p>
<lb n="0614b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b1701" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A45E;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>詣</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b18" ed="T"/>　二字</p>
<lb n="0614b19" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b1901">當於舌端而作觀想若聞。</p>
<lb n="0614b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b2001" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4BC;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00768;</zi><sg type="fangie">仁齊切</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b21" ed="T"/>　二字</p>
<lb n="0614b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b2201">當於二耳輪而作觀想。</p>
<lb n="0614b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b2301">復次修瑜伽行者若欲觀想此佛母般若波羅
<lb n="0614b24" ed="T"/>蜜多大明文字應當諦誠於自心上觀想八葉
<lb n="0614b25" ed="T"/>大紅蓮華成曼拏羅於八葉位分布觀想大明
<lb n="0614b26" ed="T"/>文字是諸文字各於方位不相間雜於蓮華東
<lb n="0614b27" ed="T"/>葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614b2801" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5ED;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>謨</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614b29" ed="T"/>　二字</p>
<pb n="0614c" id="T20.1152.0614c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0614c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c0101">於東南葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c02" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c0201" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi">婆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00344;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A55D;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>帝</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c03" ed="T"/>　四字</p>
<lb n="0614c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c0401">於南葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c0501" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">阿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA47;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>哩也</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AABC;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00425;囉</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0A4;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>倪也</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>播</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">囉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E7;</t><t lang="chi">彌</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>多</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0614c07" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c08" ed="T"/>　九字</p>
<lb n="0614c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c0901">於西南葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c1001" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">阿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">波</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E7;</t><t lang="chi">彌</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A45C;</t><t lang="chi">虞</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A54B;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>拏</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c11" ed="T"/>　八字</p>
<lb n="0614c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c1201">於西葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c1301" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5D9;</t><t lang="chi">薄</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E04D;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>訖底</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">蹉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64B;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>邏</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c14" ed="T"/>　六字</p>
<lb n="0614c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c1501">於西北葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c1601" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">薩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B7A3;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>哩&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>他</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A458;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00344;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0A4;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>倪也</zi><sg>二合引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">波</t></tt>
<lb n="0614c17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0614c18" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi">哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E042;</t><t lang="chi">布</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi">哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c19" ed="T"/>　十四字</p>
<lb n="0614c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c2001">於北葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c2101" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">薩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">埵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">蹉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64B;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>邏</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt>
<lb n="0614c22" ed="T"/>　六字</p>
<lb n="0614c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c2301">於東北葉位想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c2401" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">怛</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A7EF;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00853;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A564;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>他</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c25" ed="T"/>　三字</p>
<lb n="0614c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c2601">此八葉位次第想已於蓮華中心當想安布。</p>
<lb n="0614c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c2701" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E074;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>唵</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1D5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>提</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0614c28" ed="T"/>二字</p>
<lb n="0614c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0614c2901">復於蓮華內圍想分布八位於東位想。</p>
<pb n="0615a" id="T20.1152.0615a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0615a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a0101" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AB61;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>率嚕</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a02" ed="T"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a0301">東南位想。</p>
<lb n="0615a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a0401" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4E8;</t><t lang="chi">底</t></tt>
<lb n="0615a05" ed="T"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a0601">南位想。</p>
<lb n="0615a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a0701" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B2CE;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑蜜哩</zi><sg>三<note n="0615001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（一字）本文【三】</note><note n="0615001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合＋（一字）本文【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0615001"><lem>合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">合一字</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0615a08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0615a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a0901">西南位想。</p>
<lb n="0615a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a1001" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47E;</t><t lang="chi">底</t></tt>
<lb n="0615a11" ed="T"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a1201">西位想。</p>
<lb n="0615a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a1301" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A658;</t><t lang="chi">尾</t></tt>
<lb n="0615a14" ed="T"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a15" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a1501">西北位想。</p>
<lb n="0615a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a1601" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4B6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>惹</zi><sg type="fangie">仁左切</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a17" ed="T"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a18" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a1801">北位想。</p>
<lb n="0615a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a1901" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曳</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a20" ed="T"/>一字</p>
<lb n="0615a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a2101">東北位想。</p>
<lb n="0615a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a2201" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA49;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>莎</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0615a23" ed="T"/>二字</p>
<lb n="0615a24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0615a2401">如是觀想大明文字。各安布已。即當依法諦
<lb n="0615a25" ed="T"/>想文字真理法門。或復依法憶念持誦。於日
<lb n="0615a26" ed="T"/>三時依法布壇。<note n="0615002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持＝特【宋】</note><app n="0615002"><lem>持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">特</rdg></app>誦一百八遍。或一千八十
<lb n="0615a27" ed="T"/>遍。若一月或六月。乃至一年不間斷者。即得
<lb n="0615a28" ed="T"/>最上勝悉地法。又復若聞若持若誦者。是人
<lb n="0615a29" ed="T"/>當得聞持具足證空三摩地。如是佛母般若
<pb n="0615b" id="T20.1152.0615b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0615b01" ed="T"/>波羅蜜多大明。最上甚深有大功德。修瑜伽
<lb n="0615b02" ed="T"/>者<note n="0615003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">應＋（當）【三】</note><note n="0615003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應＋（當）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0615003"><lem>應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">應當</rdg></app>依法如是觀想。</p>
<lb n="0615b03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說佛母般若波羅蜜多大明觀想儀<app source="0614003" type="＊"><lem>軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">軌經</rdg></app></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>